data.description: Your search is over!Awesome Spacious floorplan home nestled on a desired corner lot of a cul-de-sac! This one-story residence provides a 3-car garage that lets you bring all your cars & toys. Come inside to find an open layout with tile flooring throughout & abundant natural light, allowing the dining & living areas to flow perfectly. The kitchen showcases built-in appliances, a two-tiered island w/breakfast bar, granite counters, wood cabinets, a pantry, mosaic backsplash, & recessed lighting. The split primary bedroom is a true retreat with its walk-in closet & ensuite boasting a dual sink vanity. In the backyard, you'll discover a covered patio with extended pavers & pergola, a tree planted in the yard that will continue to mature to add privacy, & space for hosting gatherings.
